; --- Legend A (Nesut / Pharaoh) conditions ---
; Natural path. Balanced stats + Fame. A casual player who does shows
; and trains reasonably will hit this. Thresholds set so that a player
; who trains varied and attends shows naturally qualifies mid-career.

[sub_resource type="Resource" id="la_1"]
