hint_vague = "Something happens when the crowd doesn't warm to them..."
hint_full = "Needs Charisma below 180"

; --- Legend C (Aten-Ka / God-King) conditions ---
; Against-grain path. All six stats above threshold AND a championship win.
; The championship requirement means you can't just train in a gym — you must
; compete. A player who stumbles into balanced stats but never wins a title
; will NOT hit this path. Requires intentional engagement with the show system.
; hint_vague is "???" — this path is deliberately obscure.

